PrecisOrder making known that the Governor in Council, having considered a petition to set aside a decision (CRTC 93-324) rendered by the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission concerning the acquisition by CHUM Limited of the assets of CKKW and CFCA-FM Kitchener from Electrohome Limited, declines to set it aside or to refer it back to the Commission for reconsideration and hearing.
